Rabat,0wpM-X5jSkI,UgysHzs7oRmP6niFbEh4AaABAg,,@Boug0014,"The flag you were referring to, is the Amazigh Flag.  The symbol in the middle ⵣ is Aza or letter Z in Tifinagh or Amazigh scripts which is in the middle of the word AmaZigh and symbolizes the Amazigh people, the natives of North Africa.  The colors of the flag symbolizes the North African geography, Blue for the Mediterranean and the Atlantic, the green for the forests in the Atlas mountains and the yellow for the Sahara desert.",2026-04-18T01:29:14Z,2026-04-18T01:29:14Z,0,False,1.0,2026-04-26T09:52:22.296793
