Tourism,cSHqVU3-DgA,UgypqPtCVvDoTvv0NwR4AaABAg,,@kimh,"In the case of the Netherlands expressing a liking for Canadians, I can say this is a continuing gratitude for playing the largest role in 1944-45 in liberating the country from Nazi occupation. The USA, Britain and the free Polish army also participated, but the Canadians still get most of the appreciation. My parents met that way (she was a war bride, Dad was a Canadian soldier) and on a trip to the Netherlands in 2016, we felt that warmth.",2026-04-26T02:02:37Z,2026-04-26T02:02:37Z,0,False,0.0,2026-04-26T09:53:14.277035
Tourism,cSHqVU3-DgA,UgxPgETIbaLp_aau8ul4AaABAg,,@L33tSkE3t,"American here, I’m tired of my own country’s citizens. I’m sick of loud and confidently ignorant people who have never taken a second to educate themselves about literally anything, thinking they actually know what’s going on in our own country. When I’ve actually asked these people (I think many can imagine what kind of American I’m talking about) why they think these objectively abhorrent things, I’m met with a line of dribble, incoherent thoughts, outright bigotry, or some conspiracy theory based on nothing but vibes. When pointing out the ridiculousness of these things, I’m then met with, “I’m entitled to my opinion,” and it takes everything I have to not reply with, “yes, you are certainly entitled.” I don’t go abroad often, one because I’m a chronically ill individual living in private healthcare dystopia, but also because I’m too embarrassed to. We Americans are basically indoctrinated from a very young age to be “patriotic” (Nationalistic is closer to what it really is) and it has likely made too many of us insufferable to be around. Add the political climate that’s existed in America since around 2017 as well as my county’s recent hostility to some of our closest allies (especially Canada, seriously us Americans need to become famous for apologizing to Canadians for how we’ve betrayed their friendship and trust as a nation) and this news of Americans being unwelcome isn’t at all surprising.",2026-04-26T01:36:16Z,2026-04-26T01:48:30Z,0,False,0.0,2026-04-26T09:53:14.277040
