Tourism,cSHqVU3-DgA,UgxTYdKd_ZO1iGoT1uJ4AaABAg.AVpR0HbDbu2AVpzLUFmEa8,UgxTYdKd_ZO1iGoT1uJ4AaABAg,@inannaliban,"I actually bought an American and his wife a Costco lunch the other day.  Fun fact, American Costco uses Visa, we use Mastercard.  Although the Visa will work at the gas pumps, it will not work in the store, or at the concession.  When he realized he couldn't pay I reached over and tapped my card to pay.  It was only $5.  He tried to hand me some bills and I laughed and said I did not want American money and asked where he was from?  He told me Alaska, and that he apologized for his government.  I told him he could now tell people a Canadian Witch bought him lunch at a Prince George Costco (I wear a pointy hat), lol.",2026-04-20T20:25:36Z,2026-04-20T20:25:36Z,15,True,,2026-04-26T09:53:14.675821
