3.tiktok streamers and nuisanse streamers. I just call them nuisance streamers.. usually women and yeah some get called out on it and if some grannies see it they hose you down with with the waterhose. People over here in Europe do not like to be filmed.
4. prank streamers. Same as nuisance streamers but it has gotten out of hand SO MUCH that certain cities have banned those people alltogether and if locals are annoyed they can use those laws to have you arrested and pay a fine. Why a different catagory? because there are actual local laws in place for that. Most of them are either American or British ( its one of the reasons why british get a lot of hate in Spain because some did it there 2 and then spain has a 100% tax on all properties for British and english speakers.. so if you buy a house in say Andalusia ant its 120 000 ( for a smaller house) you as a brit or american will pay 240 000euros. Why? because by purchasing property there you are denying a Spanish person from buying it ( anti gentrification laws). its a direct result of points 1-4.
5. americans going to europe to eff women some even going after underage girls. Yeah you will get issues and beatings regardless what country you are going to in the rest of the world.

As for Amsterdam i believe its stopping airbnb because tourists book those so much that locals cant rent places and have to go live further and further away. The ""stay away tourists"" is not general it specific to airbnb people or people that use airbnb and not the hotels. its a form of gentrification. Madrid has the same issues. France has it too especially Paris.",2026-04-21T00:34:41Z,2026-04-21T00:34:41Z,1,True,,2026-04-26T09:53:14.675845
