Maroc,Q3s8L_fjHjU,Ugw0CzgjeD7kkfj2aK94AaABAg.ATTA9Mjv1W0AU3IRJHqsGw,Ugw0CzgjeD7kkfj2aK94AaABAg,@kristinalewis6126,i started but got triggered/  sigh  i was thrown from a horse at the the beach  almost drown  went to a private hospital had surgery was treated with such kindness and so taken care of  no one spoke english  i was there for 3 weeks then flown home to the us  the hospitals in america should be ashamed of the way they treat patients.  when i left i asked if they wanted my amex number for the bill and they said no we can tell you are an honest person you will pay  6 weeks later the insurance covered the whole bill  $22k made out to me  lol  i immediately sent a check to the dr.  that is like a day in the hospital here.  i broke my femur in 3 places including one compound and my hip.  i had a lot of Moroccan blood transfused.  i have a longer version,2026-03-07T16:47:44Z,2026-03-07T16:47:44Z,4,True,,2026-04-26T09:54:05.026909
