Maroc,Q3s8L_fjHjU,UgyZppuLZA3hxEnIn2x4AaABAg.ATIK5Qi7mf2ATIS_dnUIru,UgyZppuLZA3hxEnIn2x4AaABAg,@TraceTheGlobe,That’s incredibly touching. 🇲🇦❤ Do you ever think about visiting again to relive those memories?,2026-02-16T17:33:37Z,2026-02-16T17:33:37Z,1,True,,2026-04-26T09:54:05.936695
Maroc,Q3s8L_fjHjU,UgyZppuLZA3hxEnIn2x4AaABAg.ATIK5Qi7mf2ATNes3kaXsX,UgyZppuLZA3hxEnIn2x4AaABAg,@redwoods7370,"@TraceTheGlobe Thank you for your kind words. I am 70 now and it would be hard for me to get back to Morocco. But the vivid memory lives within my heart forever. I'd like to tell you how I know that the Moroccan people are kind and generous. My father made the mistake of driving through the desert without really knowing how vast it was. We ran out of gas and two shepherds took us dumb Americans totally under their wing, got us gas, smiled at us and took care of us in the kindest way possible. Every Moroccan person we encountered was gracious and kind. I felt that I was among true, whole and authentic human beings. I wish I had the words. God bless Morocco and its lovely people.",2026-02-18T18:05:56Z,2026-02-18T18:05:56Z,10,True,,2026-04-26T09:54:05.936711
Maroc,Q3s8L_fjHjU,UgyZppuLZA3hxEnIn2x4AaABAg.ATIK5Qi7mf2ATNhoBhTvcp,UgyZppuLZA3hxEnIn2x4AaABAg,@TraceTheGlobe,"@redwoods7370 Your story is deeply moving — thank you for sharing such a precious memory with us. 🇲🇦✨ What happened to your family in the desert is a beautiful reminder of the kindness and humanity that travel can reveal. Those shepherds may never know it, but their compassion clearly left a lifelong imprint on your heart.

We are honored that Morocco holds such a special place in your memories. Even if the journey back is difficult, the connection you carry is something no distance can ever take away.

God bless you as well — and thank you for reminding us why stories like yours matter so much. ❤",2026-02-18T18:31:37Z,2026-02-18T18:31:37Z,3,True,,2026-04-26T09:54:05.936717
